---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../lib/site';
---

<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How TrailNestCo collects, uses, and protects your information." path="/privacy-policy" updated="June 1, 2026">
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how {SITE.business.legalName} ("{SITE.name}," "we," "us") collects, uses,
    and discloses information when you visit {SITE.domain}.
  </p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, time on site, referring URLs, and device/browser information, collected via analytics tools.</li>
    <li><strong>Information you provide</strong> — name and email address if you contact us, subscribe to a newsletter, or submit a pitch.</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies &amp; similar technologies</strong> — used for analytics, remembering preferences, and measuring affiliate link performance.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To operate, maintain, and improve the site and our content</li>
    <li>To respond to inquiries sent to our contact addresses</li>
    <li>To measure which articles and affiliate links perform well, in aggregate and anonymized form</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Affiliate links &amp; third parties</h2>
  <p>
    When you click an affiliate link, the destination retailer or affiliate network (e.g. Awin, Impact, CJ
    Affiliate) may set its own cookies and collect data according to its own privacy policy. We encourage
    you to review the privacy policy of any third-party site you visit. See our
    <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for more detail.
  </p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <p>
    Most browsers let you block or delete cookies through their settings. Doing so may affect site
    functionality. Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, or delete personal
    data we hold about you — contact us to make a request.
  </p>

  <h2>Data retention &amp; security</h2>
  <p>
    We retain contact information only as long as needed to respond to your inquiry or fulfill the purpose
    it was collected for, and use reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect it.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>{SITE.name} is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from them.</p>

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy periodically. Material changes will be reflected by an updated "Last updated" date above.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    {SITE.business.legalName}<br />
    {SITE.business.addressFull}<br />
    <a href={`mailto:${SITE.business.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.business.contactEmail}</a> &middot;
    <a href={SITE.business.phoneHref}>{SITE.business.phone}</a>
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
